Subset Dataset

In[7]:
# Select specific cell annotations of interest
desired_annotations <- c("Intermediate B", "Memory B", "Naive B")
In[8]:
# Extract cell IDs that belong to the desired annotations
cells_of_interest <- colnames(coembed)[
  coembed@meta.data$seurat_annotations %in% desired_annotations
]
In[9]:
# Set a seed for reproducibility and randomly sample 200 cells from the selected annotation groups
set.seed(123)  
sampled_cells <- sample(cells_of_interest, size = 200, replace = FALSE)
In[10]:
# Add a new metadata column "select" initialized to 0 for all cells
coembed <- AddMetaData(coembed, metadata = rep(0, ncol(coembed)), col.name = "select")
# Mark the sampled cells by setting "select" to 1
coembed@meta.data[sampled_cells, "select"] <- 1
# Display count of selected cells
table(coembed$select)

    0     1 
20624   200
